---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative flex items-center justify-center px-5 h-screen overflow-hidden pb-0 pt-32 md:pt-40"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 w-full h-full overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="/images/masjid-interior.webp"
      alt="Masjid Interior"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute -inset-5 w-[110%] h-[110%] bg-black/20"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-40 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-black/40 to-black"></div>

  <div class="relative text-center z-10 max-w-lg md:max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-6xl text-white" style="line-height: 1.5">
      إِنَّنِىٓ أَنَا ٱللَّهُ لَآ إِلَـٰهَ إِلَّآ أَنَا۠ فَٱعْبُدْنِى وَأَقِمِ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ لِذِكْرِىٓ
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-white text-3xl">
      Indeed, I am Allāh. There is no deity except Me, so worship Me and establish prayer for My remembrance.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-white text-2xl italic">
      — Surah Tāhā, 20:14 (Saheeh International)
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
